          "process_md": "&amp;gt; **Registration**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Official Website](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Website/LabourReg.aspx) of the Bihar Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board, and click &amp;amp;quot;[Apply for New Registration](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Registration/AddLabourRegistrationWeb.aspx)&amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 4:** On the next page, provide your details including your Aadhaar Number. Then click &amp;amp;quot;Authenticate&amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 5:** An online form will appear. In the form, fill in all the mandatory fields. The fields marked with an asterisk (*) are mandatory.\n**Step 6:** Click &amp;amp;quot;Submit&amp;amp;quot;. Proceed to pay the application fee online.\n**Step 7:****** Upon successful payment, you will receive your construction worker registration number.\n&amp;gt; **Application**\n\n**Step 1:****** Visit the [Official Website ](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Website/SchemeApply.aspx)of the Bihar Building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board.\n**Step 2:** Click on &amp;amp;quot;[Scheme Application](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Website/SchemeApply.aspx)&amp;amp;quot; and select &amp;amp;quot;[Apply for Scheme](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Registration/SchemeTaggingWeb.aspx)&amp;amp;quot;.\n**Step 3:****** Enter your registration number and click &amp;amp;quot;Show&amp;amp;quot; to view your details.\n**Step 4:****** Select the scheme you intend to apply for, enter all mandatory information and upload the necessary documents in the specified format and size.\n**Step 6:****** Click on &amp;amp;quot;Submit Application&amp;amp;quot; to complete the process.\n&amp;gt; **Application Tracking**\n\nApplicants can track their application status online on the [official website ](https://bocw.bihar.gov.in/Registration/ApplicationStatus.aspx)of the Board by providing their registration number.\n"
        }
